&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Care Support Worker – NHS Professionals &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We currently have some unique and exciting opportunities within &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Manchester Foundation Trust&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; which will allow the successful candidates to gain &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;regular shifts&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; and valuable &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;experience&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; within a variety of community hospital settings. We have both &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Fully Flexible Ad Hoc shifts&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; allowing you to choose when you want to work!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note that due to the urgency of these vacancies, we are actively looking for CSWs who do already have hospital experience. Please bare this in mind prior to applying. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a completley flexible placement - we can offer a variety of shift patterns and a variety of wards too including surgical wards, Covid wards and orthopaedic wards too. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more information, please contact Sophie Goodman on sophie.goodman@nhsprofessionals.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
